Name: python-module-%oname
Version: 4.2.0
#Release: alt3.1
Summary: Principal-searching UI for Zope 3 Pluggable Authentication
License: ZPLv2.1
Group: Development/Python
Url: http://pypi.python.org/pypi/zc.security/
